!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta{content: "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
  %body
    %p
      Dear #{@participant.first_name.titleize}
    %p
      #{@participant.full_name} has shared a file with you through the DRIVE online tool.
    %p
      First Name: #{@participant.first_name}
    %p
      Last Name: #{@participant.last_name}
    %p
      Email: #{@participant.email}
    %p
      Job Title: #{@participant.job_title}
    %p
      Division: #{@participant.division}
    %p
      Year Started: #{@participant.year_started}
    %p
      You’ll find a copy of the file attached to this email, and it’s also stored in the My Files section of your DRIVE online tool.
    %p
      To upload and share your own files, simply visit the My Files section and choose a participant from your DRIVE network.

    %p
      Thanks
      %br/
      DRIVE Support